<br>
Replace the Cougar Claw with a Wolf Fang. If you sell the Cougar Claw, this may cost you nothing, and stamina is more useful than dexterity.<br>
<br>
Replace the rings with AC6 HP65 rings. Doing both fingers should cost you well under 1000pp. If you are ambitious, you could instead try to hunt for a Shadel Bandit Ring for one finger.<br>
<br>
Get some Deepwater Boots. That's just a lot of AC to give up. On Drinal you'd get those for under 1000, most likely.<br>
<br>
The last obvious thing I might do is to replace your bp with Barbed Ringmail. On Drinal that would run you about 4k or so these days if you were patient. It all depends what you think your prospects are for getting a drop. If you do Fear, Thurg, whatever often, and thing you might see a drop, stick it out. If not, it will be a nice upgrade.<br>
<br>
There are plenty of other things you could do, but these jump out at me, and even if you did everything I suggest, you'd still have plenty of cash left over.<br>
<br>
